:"28819e108b7de7c92e784d4c89c24d234fe2050b","tid":2078073,"uid":1699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"後來，她擔任過中共平順縣委副書記。1973年，出任山西省婦聯主任。在出任婦聯主任初期，她曾赴太原就職，但發現實在無事可做。有位新華社記者為她出主意稱，主任繼續當，但只在開會時來太原，平時則繼續在西溝村勞動。申紀蘭同他人商量後，採用了該辦法，僅到婦聯「坐會」，開完會後便回西溝村。<br />\n<br />\n其實即係乜鳩都唔識但又要坐住個位 令個社會0進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1473e5c296818853e4bde3493dd1532b80edabe8","tid":2078073,"uid":336429,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"90歲阿婆都可以用嚟打飛機,不愧兒登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f102c70c327c56a04b58b15a66ec9892e0881d","tid":2078073,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51422351c4d1e447987a500ce08f80b9e1c16304","tid":2078073,"uid":19165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:03:16.000Z","msg":"成世人流流長終於有機會可以做返一件好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd37f8e8629396150501ecaf9a332baa77cccb1","tid":2078073,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"中左武漢肺炎，張相隔離條友都淨係戴口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e7188852526df21a971c8b79fa4bbc7c1f016e","tid":2078073,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"次次都投票支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定係karma"},{"pid":"d6e936b485a7d08e83935c8b468a1f74d220c932","tid":2078073,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"大紀元打飛機 拉"},{"pid":"8c14dd3f950a7c14340610b4887e3cd19fddce8b","tid":2078073,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"