":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"呢條友死得好<br />\n<br />\n典型中國人渣"},{"pid":"0423401a9a5ec98eabb29186090dc14d415797e5","tid":2078073,"uid":277037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"For唔識佢嘅巴打：<br />\n2010年，申紀蘭表示：「我非常擁護共產黨。當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」這一言論引發了廣泛的社會爭論。而申紀蘭則在2011年回應稱，作為人民代表大會制度的見證人，內心擁護的事，她就贊成，不擁護的，她就不投票。媒體引述，其被民間戲稱為「舉手機器」、「人大活化石」<br />\n唔知佢死個陣隻閪手係咪都係舉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4374c19aa057850ce4990c82b0cefb18f60952e","tid":2078073,"uid":353489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"得一件咋... 有冇多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c19c75f34ff296e25dd9238310f9e93515f3d57","tid":2078073,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701d8c0acdac62e20cf07d9c71811934cc34ebc9","tid":2078073,"uid":54975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"睇相以為係痰喂豬，開心咗半秒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc8b5d49211d6e5dc8a261a953dcde3696195c4","tid":2078073,"uid":251961,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0423401a9a5ec98eabb29186090dc14d415797e5","tid":2078073,"uid":277037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"For唔識佢嘅巴打：<br />\n2010年，申紀蘭表示：「我非常擁護共產黨。當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」這一言論引發了廣泛的社會爭論。而申紀蘭則在2011年回應稱，作為人民代表大會制度的見證人，內心擁護的事，她就贊成，不擁護的，她就不投票。媒體引述，其被民間戲稱為「舉手機器」、「人大活化石」<br />\n唔知佢死個陣隻閪手係咪都係舉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"最經典：<br />\n<br />\n記者問：「您平常跟選民有交流嗎？在選舉的時候跟選民有交流嗎？」<br />\n申紀蘭回答：「我沒有，我們這是靠民主選舉的，你交流就不合適」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f062cb00cfcbaa88dead133aacb551242e08ea","tid":2078073,"uid":160534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"快撚d死撚晒佢"},{"pid":"1d31f46781ffaae157b4749271275d6952bcab85","tid":2078073,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c7853566b0b797fa45ccffab6a94441c5329162","tid":2078073,"uid":47674,"like":201,"dislike":0,"score":201,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"個樣仲好精神呀<br />\n冇事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a62a9654dc8a50a8ab9a65a357444203b83076","tid":2078073,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8286a9c9bf15810dd3499a7d2c14abef6b8be5","tid":2078073,"uid":83713,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"2010年中共兩會期間，申紀蘭曾公開說：「當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」申紀蘭因此被譏為「舉手機器」。<br />\n<br />\n申紀蘭每次「當選」，都引來網民嘲諷。中國政法大學法學院副院長何兵譏諷其「前無古人，後無來者」。著名律師袁裕來乾脆稱其為「化石級的人大代表」。<br />\n<br />\n有民眾表示：「申紀蘭現象是這個體制的象徵、是偉光正的特色、是對人民代表的諷刺、是大陸這個時代的見證！」<br />\n<br />\n還有民眾表示，「申紀蘭能連任，就因為她贊成。她贊成大躍進，贊成人民公社，贊成文革，贊成鬥劉少奇，贊成否定大躍進，贊成否定人民公社，贊成否定文革，贊成平反劉少奇。其實，她只是個縮影，我們只要弄清楚：她為何要贊成？是誰讓她贊成？她敢不敢不贊成？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"人大代表唔係聽人民意見 而係完全聽從黨<br />\n中國特色民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7bb78103ccb1f915451f44f19ce62ab8698c4e","tid":2078073,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"就死都要維持含撚嘴 做左共產黨慰安婦太耐"},{"pid":"891574ef2112cbf5423b32cae87f12f2189215cf","tid":2078073,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事<br />\n佢係個好有愛嘅黨員，希望佢感染畀多啲同志"},{"pid":"e2f6a291ba7240bacfccfe53ef11b0fe9e4fd820","tid":2078073,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc8b5d49211d6e5dc8a261a953dcde3696195c4","tid":2078073,"uid":251961,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0423401a9a5ec98eabb29186090dc14d415797e5","tid":2078073,"uid":277037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"For唔識佢嘅巴打：<br />\n2010年，申紀蘭表示：「我非常擁護共產黨。當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」這一言論引發了廣泛的社會爭論。而申紀蘭則在2011年回應稱，作為人民代表大會制度的見證人，內心擁護的事，她就贊成，不擁護的，她就不投票。媒體引述，其被民間戲稱為「舉手機器」、「人大活化石」<br />\n唔知佢死個陣隻閪手係咪都係舉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"最經典：<br />\n<br />\n記者問：「您平常跟選民有交流嗎？在選舉的時候跟選民有交流嗎？」<br />\n申紀蘭回答：「我沒有，我們這是靠民主選舉的，你交流就不合適」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">你</span></span>民<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我</span></span>主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e25da74301ca1b3c10497627c475a487345aedf","tid":2078073,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a62a9654dc8a50a8ab9a65a357444203b83076","tid":2078073,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8286a9c9bf15810dd3499a7d2c14abef6b8be5","tid":2078073,"uid":83713,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"2010年中共兩會期間，申紀蘭曾公開說：「當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」申紀蘭因此被譏為「舉手機器」。<br />\n<br />\n申紀蘭每次「當選」，都引來網民嘲諷。中國政法大學法學院副院長何兵譏諷其「前無古人，後無來者」。著名律師袁裕來乾脆稱其為「化石級的人大代表」。<br />\n<br />\n有民眾表示：「申紀蘭現象是這個體制的象徵、是偉光正的特色、是對人民代表的諷刺、是大陸這個時代的見證！」<br />\n<br />\n還有民眾表示，「申紀蘭能連任，就因為她贊成。她贊成大躍進，贊成人民公社，贊成文革，贊成鬥劉少奇，贊成否定大躍進，贊成否定人民公社，贊成否定文革，贊成平反劉少奇。其實，她只是個縮影，我們只要弄清楚：她為何要贊成？是誰讓她贊成？她敢不敢不贊成？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"人大代表唔係聽人民意見 而係完全聽從黨<br />\n中國特色民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"黨話佢代表人民 所以佢講乜都係代表人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b9518f0d968ed5f561c259c2a677e7d4d5c76a","tid":2078073,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09a62a9654dc8a50a8ab9a65a357444203b83076","tid":2078073,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8286a9c9bf15810dd3499a7d2c14abef6b8be5","tid":2078073,"uid":83713,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"2010年中共兩會期間，申紀蘭曾公開說：「當代表就是要聽黨的話，我從來沒有投過反對票。」申紀蘭因此被譏為「舉手機器」。<br />\n<br /